select count(*) as aggregate from `listings` where (`make_id` = '15' or exists (select * from `makes` where `listings`.`make_id` = `makes`.`id` and `name` like '%15%')) and `status` = 1

select `listings`.*, (select count(*) from `visits` where `listings`.`id` = `visits`.`visitable_id` and `visits`.`visitable_type` = 'App\Models\Listing') as `visit_logs_count` from `listings` where (`make_id` = '15' or exists (select * from `makes` where `listings`.`make_id` = `makes`.`id` and `name` like '%15%')) and `status` = 1 order by `id` asc, `visit_logs_count` desc, `is_featured` desc, `is_certified` desc, `is_single_owner` desc, `is_well_equipped` desc, `no_accident` desc, `is_city_mpg_verified` desc, `is_highway_mpg_verified` desc, `mileage` asc, `is_mileage_verified` desc, `is_negotiated` desc, `year` desc, `created_at` desc limit 8 offset 0

select `features`.*, `feature_listing`.`listing_id` as `pivot_listing_id`, `feature_listing`.`feature_id` as `pivot_feature_id` from `features` inner join `feature_listing` on `features`.`id` = `feature_listing`.`feature_id` where `feature_listing`.`listing_id` in (5)
select `id`, `name` from `makes` where exists (select * from `listings` where `makes`.`id` = `listings`.`make_id`)
select * from `language_lines` where `group` = 'Show only ad with video'
select * from `media` where `media`.`model_type` = 'App\Models\Listing' and `media`.`model_id` = 5 and `media`.`model_id` is not null
select * from `language_lines` where `group` = 'Subscribe to our newsletter'
select * from `language_lines` where `group` = 'Don’t miss any relevant offers!'
